      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is in great shape with only minor signs of use, such as small rock chips on the hood, while the interior remains clean and comfortable with no major stains or tears. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
